WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Half grand chain, crossing RH with partner to start

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.000
Turn partner RH

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Turn partner LH

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:19.000
1C &amp; 3C advance, clink glasses with opposite, retire

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:24.000
1C &amp; 3C set, cross RH -while- 2C &amp; 4C advance, clink, chase ccw

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:31.000
1C with 2C, and 3C with 4C dance double figures of 8 (1C&amp;3C casting and 2C&amp;4C crossing RH to start)

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Finish in a longwise set (3-4-2-1), 4C&amp;1C on partners' side

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:41.000
Ladies dance towards &amp; RSh around partner, pass whisky, retire

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:51.000
Ladies set to partners with Highland setting step

00:00:51.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Men dance towards &amp; RSh around partner, pass both glasses, retire

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Men set to partners with Highland setting step

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:11.000
1C &amp; 3C advance -while- 2C &amp; 4C dance half turn w/o hands, return whisky, all retire

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:17.000
1C with 2C, and 3C with 4C dance RH across, 2M &amp; 4M peel off, finish in double RH star

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:25.000
Dance double RH star. Finish in square set opposite original places.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:34.500
Half grand chain, crossing RH with partner to start

00:01:34.500 --> 00:01:38.000
Turn partner RH

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:45.000
Turn partner LH

